content: प्रपत् {c1c} <ab>P.</ab> {@--1@} To fly forth or away., {@--2@} To fly, fly or move about. {@--3@} To fall down or upon, throw oneself down. {@--4@} To hasten towards. {@--5@} To be deprived of, fall from, lose, fall off or away from. {@--6@} To come down, fall down, descend. {%--<ab>Caus.</ab>%} {@--1@} To throw down. {@--2@} To rout, put to flight. {@--3@} To chase, pursue.
